description: Well used trail climbs steady from parking lot to about 3.5 kms. At this point the trail levels for about .5 km then drops into a valley by a pond. You then make the final climb to the summit. 360 deg views at summit.
directions: Take route 16 cutoff from route 299 near Gîte du Mont-Albert and follow signage to trail head
title: Mont Richardson-Gaspesie
